{"id": "art-4111", "label": "Art. 4111", "title": "Art. 4111: Date şi informaţii privind categoriile de personal cuprinse în Sistemul electronic naţional de evidenţă a ocupării în sectorul public", "slug": "art-4111", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2005398846\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1280\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2005398846\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 411<sup>1</sup>:\nDate &#351;i informa&#355;ii privind categoriile de personal cuprinse în\nSistemul electronic na&#355;ional de eviden&#355;&#259; a ocup&#259;rii în\nsectorul public </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_804191195\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1279\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_804191195\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Sistemul\nelectronic na&#355;ional de eviden&#355;&#259; a ocup&#259;rii în sectorul\npublic se constituie în form&#259; electronic&#259; &#351;i cuprinde date\n&#351;i informa&#355;ii despre categoriile de personal pl&#259;tit din fonduri\npublice prev&#259;zute la lit. a) &#351;i c)-f), respectiv date statistice\ndespre categoriile de personal prev&#259;zute la lit. b) &#351;i g), dup&#259;\ncum urmeaz&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1691475817\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1278\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1691475817\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)func&#355;ionarii publici care de&#355;in func&#355;ii\npublice generale &#351;i func&#355;ii publice specifice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_319742792\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1277\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_319742792\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)func&#355;ionarii publici cu statut special din cadrul\nautorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i institu&#355;iilor publice prev&#259;zute la\nart. 380 alin. (1) lit. f);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_335985004\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1276\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_335985004\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)personalul pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice încadrat cu\ncontract individual de munc&#259; sau contract de management din familia\nocupa&#355;ional&#259; de func&#355;ii bugetare «Administra&#355;ie», precum\n&#351;i cel care exercit&#259; un mandat corespunz&#259;tor unei func&#355;ii\nde demnitate public&#259;, astfel cum este prev&#259;zut în\nlegisla&#355;ia-cadru privind salarizarea personalului pl&#259;tit din fonduri\npublice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1705941786\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1275\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1705941786\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)personalul pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice din familia\nocupa&#355;ional&#259; de func&#355;ii bugetare «Înv&#259;&#355;&#259;mânt»,\ndin familia ocupa&#355;ional&#259; de func&#355;ii bugetare «S&#259;n&#259;tate\n&#351;i asisten&#355;&#259; social&#259;», din familia ocupa&#355;ional&#259;\nde func&#355;ii bugetare «Cultur&#259;», astfel cum sunt prev&#259;zute în\nlegisla&#355;ia-cadru privind salarizarea personalului pl&#259;tit din fonduri\npublice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1300614776\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1274\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1300614776\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)personalul contractual angajat în afara organigramei\nautorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice, pl&#259;tit din bugetele\nproiectelor, care desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activit&#259;&#355;i în cadrul\nprogramelor/proiectelor cu finan&#355;are extern&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1830479873\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1273\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1830479873\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)personalul pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice încadrat cu\ncontract individual de munc&#259; care î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259;\nactivitatea în cadrul autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i institu&#355;iilor\npublice finan&#355;ate integral din venituri proprii, aflate în subordinea, sub\nautoritatea, în coordonarea Guvernului, ministerelor &#351;i a celorlalte\norgane de specialitate ale administra&#355;iei publice centrale &#351;i locale,\ndin cele aflate în coordonarea prim-ministrului, precum &#351;i din cele aflate\nsub controlul Parlamentului, astfel cum este prev&#259;zut în legisla&#355;ia- cadru\nprivind salarizarea personalului pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1915889687\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1272\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1915889687\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)personalul pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice prev&#259;zut\nla art. 411 alin. (8<sup>1</sup>).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1938145384\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1271\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1938145384\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Sistemul\nelectronic na&#355;ional de eviden&#355;&#259; a ocup&#259;rii în sectorul\npublic cuprinde urm&#259;toarele date &#351;i informa&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1173585176\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1270\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1173585176\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)datele de identificare ale fiec&#259;rei\nautorit&#259;&#355;i &#351;i institu&#355;ii publice, precum &#351;i ale\npersoanelor juridice în cadrul c&#259;rora î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259;\nactivitatea categoriile de personal prev&#259;zute în legisla&#355;ia-cadru\nprivind salarizarea personalului pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_820459946\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1269\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_820459946\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)date &#351;i informa&#355;ii cu privire la fiecare post\ndin sistemul bugetar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_806590376\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1268\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_806590376\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)informa&#355;ii cuprinse în fi&#351;a postului, cu\nprivire la: studii de specialitate, cerin&#355;e specifice, vechimea în\nspecialitate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1230859464\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1267\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1230859464\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)datele de identificare ale fiec&#259;rei persoane care\nface parte din categoria personalului bugetar pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice,\nrespectiv: numele, prenumele, codul numeric personal - CNP, localitatea &#351;i\njude&#355;ul de domiciliu;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1044270131\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1266\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1044270131\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)num&#259;rul &#351;i data emiterii actului administrativ\nindividual de numire, respectiv num&#259;rul &#351;i data încheierii\ncontractului individual de munc&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz, a contractului de\nmanagement, precum &#351;i data începerii activit&#259;&#355;ii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_661993329\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1265\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_661993329\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)func&#355;ia conform specifica&#355;iei prev&#259;zute în\nactul normativ prin care este reglementat&#259;, Clasific&#259;rii\nocupa&#355;iilor din România (COR) sau altor acte normative;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1861061673\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1264\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1861061673\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)durata raportului de serviciu, a mandatului\ncorespunz&#259;tor func&#355;iei de demnitate public&#259;, a contractului\nindividual de munc&#259; sau a contractului de management, respectiv\nnedeterminat&#259;/determinat&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1184569801\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1263\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1184569801\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)durata timpului de munc&#259; &#351;i repartizarea\nacestuia, în cazul raportului de serviciu cu timp par&#355;ial &#351;i al\ncontractelor individuale de munc&#259; cu timp par&#355;ial;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_548331649\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1262\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_548331649\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)venitul salarial, definit în conformitate cu prevederile\nlegisla&#355;iei-cadru privind salarizarea personalului pl&#259;tit din fonduri\npublice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1970733755\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1261\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1970733755\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)date &#351;i informa&#355;ii cu privire la modificarea,\nsuspendarea &#351;i, dup&#259; caz, prelungirea raportului de serviciu, a\ncontractului individual de munc&#259; sau a contractului de management;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_108705651\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1260\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_108705651\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k)data &#351;i temeiul legal al încet&#259;rii raportului\nde serviciu, a mandatului corespunz&#259;tor func&#355;iei de demnitate\npublic&#259;, a contractului individual de munc&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz, a\ncontractului de management;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_364874388\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1259\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_364874388\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>l)date &#351;i informa&#355;ii cu privire la responsabilul\nde raportare pentru fiecare autoritate sau institu&#355;ie public&#259;, precum\n&#351;i pentru fiecare persoan&#259; juridic&#259; în cadrul c&#259;reia\nî&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea categoriile de personal\nprev&#259;zute în legisla&#355;ia-cadru privind salarizarea personalului\npl&#259;tit din fonduri publice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_26385667\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1258\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_26385667\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>m)date despre situa&#355;ia disciplinar&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2031676684\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1257\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2031676684\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n)date înscrise în cazierul judiciar, dup&#259; caz.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_312804226\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1256\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_312804226\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Datele statistice\ncuprinse în Sistemul electronic na&#355;ional de eviden&#355;&#259; a\nocup&#259;rii în sectorul public pentru personalul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1)\nlit. b) sunt urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1315347812\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1255\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1315347812\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)datele de identificare ale autorit&#259;&#355;ilor\n&#351;i institu&#355;iilor publice prev&#259;zute la art. 380 alin. (1) lit.\nf), în cadrul c&#259;rora î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea\nfunc&#355;ionarii publici cu statut special;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1992375434\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1254\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1992375434\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)date statistice cu privire la func&#355;ionarii publici\ncu statut special din cadrul autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i institu&#355;iilor\npublice prev&#259;zute la art. 380 alin. (1) lit. f), cuprinzând: categoria de\nfunc&#355;ii, situa&#355;ia ocup&#259;rii posturilor, respectiv: ocupat &#351;i\nvacant, categoriile de posturi, respectiv: conducere &#351;i execu&#355;ie,\nnivelul de studii, respectiv suma anual&#259; alocat&#259; cheltuielilor cu\nfunc&#355;ionarii publici cu statut special, din bugetul anual alocat\ninstitu&#355;iei publice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1124173791\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1253\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1124173791\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Categoriile de date statistice cuprinse în Sistemul\nelectronic na&#355;ional de eviden&#355;&#259; a ocup&#259;rii în sectorul\npublic pentru personalul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) lit. g) se stabilesc în\ncondi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 411 alin. (8<sup>1</sup>).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2114437907\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1252\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2114437907\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Datele &#351;i informa&#355;iile despre personalul\nbugetar pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice prev&#259;zute la alin. (2) &#351;i (3)\nse colecteaz&#259; în formatul stabilit în hot&#259;rârea Guvernului\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 411 alin. (10).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL V:Drepturi &#351;i îndatoriri</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 1:Drepturile\nfunc&#355;ionarilor publici</span></b></p>"}